Playing Desire with your loved one:

• Dare your partner
You get to choose from thousands of dares. We upload new dares on a weekly base, so you’ll always have new ideas to dare your loved one. 

• Give points
Each dare has a number of points to earn. If your loved one accepts the dare and does it, then your partner will get the points. 

• Receive dares & reach the Chil level
When you receive a dare from your loved one, you can decide if you accept it or not. If you accept the dare and you do it, you get points as well! Points will let you reach higher levels in the game and unlock the hottest challenges.

• Send eLoves by shaking your phone
Shake your phone and shorts messages will appear, choose the message you want to send to your love. Find from sweet to hot messages.

• Get badges 
You will earn badges while playing Desire. Play and see who can get more of them, you or your partner.

• Couple private chat
The couples' private chat allows you to have a completely private space between you and your loved one. Pixelate parts of your pictures before sending them and send unique stickers.

• Couple private journal
Keep in a private diary all the great moments you spend together. Was it a spicy day, a romantic day or maybe a day full of adventures?
